Class ManifestMerger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simpligility.maven.plugins.android.configuration.ManifestMerger

  • public class ManifestMerger
extends Object
    Configuration for the manifest update. This class is only the definition of the parameters that are shadowed in ManifestMergerMojo and used there.
